-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WEBGL_lose_context\"><code>WEBGL_lose_context</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLBuffer\"><code>WebGLBuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLContextEvent\"><code>WebGLContextEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLFramebuffer\"><code>WebGLFramebuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>WebGLObject</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLProgram\"><code>WebGLProgram</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLQuery\"><code>WebGLQuery</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderbuffer\"><code>WebGLRenderbuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLSampler\"><code>WebGLSampler</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLShader\"><code>WebGLShader</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLShaderPrecisionFormat\"><code>WebGLShaderPrecisionFormat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLSync\"><code>WebGLSync</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLTexture\"><code>WebGLTexture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLTransformFeedback\"><code>WebGLTransformFeedback</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLUniformLocation\"><code>WebGLUniformLocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLVertexArrayObject\"><code>WebGLVertexArrayObject</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Das&nbsp;<strong>WebGLActiveInfo</strong>-Interface ist Teil der&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">WebGL API</a>&nbsp;und repräsentiert die Informationen der Rückgabewerte von den&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/getActiveAttrib\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.getActiveAttrib()</code></a> und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/getActiveUniform\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.getActiveUniform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Methoden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"webglactiveinfo.name_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLActiveInfo/name\"><code>WebGLActiveInfo.name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Der schreibgeschützte Name&nbsp;von der abgefragten Variable</dd>\n <dt id=\"webglactiveinfo.size_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLActiveInfo/size\"><code>WebGLActiveInfo.size</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Die schreibgeschützte Größe der abgefragten Variable</dd>\n <dt id=\"webglactiveinfo.type_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLActiveInfo/type\"><code>WebGLActiveInfo.type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Der schreibgeschützte Typ der abgefragten Variable</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Ein&nbsp;<code>WebGLActiveInfo</code>-Objekt wird von den folgenden Funktionen zurück gegeben:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/getActiveAttrib\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.getActiveAttrib()</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/getActiveUniform\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.getActiveUniform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext/getTransformFeedbackVarying\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext.getTransformFeedbackVarying()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>WebGLActiveInfo<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token function\">getActiveAttrib</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>WebGLProgram<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> program<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> GLuint index<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nWebGLActiveInfo<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token function\">getActiveUniform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>WebGLProgram<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> program<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> GLuint index<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nWebGLActiveInfo<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token function\">getTransformFeedbackVarying</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>WebGLProgram<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> program<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> GLuint index<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/registry/webgl/specs/latest/1.0/#5.11\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebGL 1.0<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'WebGLActiveInfo' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Erstmalige Definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Browser compatibility","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td>12</td>\n   <td>5.1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Available in workers</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/44\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2016-01-26.\">44</a> (44) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>25</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>12</td>\n   <td>8.1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Available in workers</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>44.0 (44) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Dieses Feature ist durch eine&nbsp;Voreinstellung deaktiviert. Zur Aktivierung setzt man in&nbsp;about:config den Wert&nbsp;gfx.offscreencanvas.enabled auf true.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/getActiveAttrib\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.getActiveAttrib()</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/getActiveUniform\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.getActiveUniform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Das WebGLActiveInfo-Interface ist Teil der WebGL API und repräsentiert die Informationen der Rückgabewerte von den WebGLRenderingContext.getActiveAttrib() und WebGLRenderingContext.getActiveUniform() (en-US) Methoden.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebGLActiveInfo","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebGLActiveInfo","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/webglactiveinfo","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/webglactiveinfo/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLActiveInfo","title":"WebGLActiveInfo"}],"pageTitle":"WebGLActiveInfo - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}